OL,3,CYellow weather warning for wind issued
OL,4,Cfor Cumbria and southern Scotland
OL,6,FA yellow weather warning for wind has
OL,7,Fbeen issued for Cumbria and southern
OL,8,FScotland.
OL,10,FThe Met Office has issued the weather
OL,11,Fwarning from 5am until 8pm on Thursday
OL,12,F12 March and say that heavy rain will
OL,13,Faccompany the strong winds.
OL,15,FThey say that some transport
OL,16,Fdisruption is possible and journey
OL,17,Ftimes expected to be longer.
OL,19,FWhat should you expect from the
OL,20,Fweather warning?
